entries.femaleVariant: You look great, Goro.
Mhm, V. Just in time.
For jobs like this? Always.
Plan's fucked beyond all recognition, yet here I am…
Wait. Any backup plan?
Hey, Goro. Wow, you look like a million eddies.
I am. Question is – you ready to face Oda again?
I'm ready. Question is, are you?
I formed this plan, did I not?
All while ignoring one crucial element – your "friend" Oda.
entries.maleVariant: All the while ignoring one crucial element – your "friend" Oda.

entries.femaleVariant: Oda is a man of honor. He would not dare raise his hand against me.
Maybe. But you're gonna be droppin' in on Hanako by surprise.
Huh, you have a point. Instinct and reflexes win out at the moments like this.
So?
So I can only hope that I am still faster than he is.
I know. And I thank you for this.
Ah, thank me once it works. Now get in position.
entries.maleVariant: Thank me once it works. Now get in position.

entries.femaleVariant: Very well. Wait for my signal.
Wait, if... If things go to shit, we got a backup plan?
entries.maleVariant: Wait. If things go to shit, we got a backup plan?

entries.femaleVariant: What do you think?
I am accused of betraying Arasaka. Soon I will try to confront the sister of the CEO in person.
There are no backup plans. This one must work.
Don't jump. There's always hope.
Goro? If you're here to jump, remember that there's help available. 'Round-the-clock hotline…
entries.maleVariant: Aw, Goro? If you're here to jump, remember that there's help available. There's a 'round-the-clock hotline…

entries.femaleVariant: Is that so? That is not how I feel.
That is not funny…
I ate what you call a scop-burger.
A-hah. Wow, what'd you think? Tasty?
entries.maleVariant: A-hah. And what'd you think? Tasty?

entries.femaleVariant: Ask the people below.
The parade will soon begin.
I advise you to examine it yourself.
I adjusted the data from Okada-san.
Our eyes and ears are in the guard room. I observed the CCTV, and I know where the sniper positions are.
There are many ways to reach them.
The first is nearby – he should not be a problem. The second is worse... You will have to climb.
As for the third, he hides on the footbridge over the street.
We are here... Hanako-sama's platform will stop here, close to the emergency exit we will use when all is done.
If this sounds dangerous, consider that I must leap to the float, enter through a window and meet Hanako-sama face-to-face.
The last is what I fear the most.
Is all this clear? Are you ready?
[Take shard]
From these points, you will have a clear view of the parade. But the snipers will see things even better.
If they notice you – BANG! No more thief.
Are you ready or not?
To begin with, the malware works, truly! Much better than I anticipated.
They are a trio. You must make each harmless... before they do the same to me.
[Wait] Stay safe.
